  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of Early Calcineurin Inhibitor Withdrawal in Primary Renal Allografts</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open Label Randomized Single Study to Evaluate the Safety &amp; Efficacy of Early CNI Withdrawal in Recipients of Primary Renal Allografts Maintained Long-Term on Mycophenolate Mofetil; MMF (CellCept) and Sirolimus (Rapamune)</official_title>
