  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the safety and efficacy of early corticosteroid withdrawal and simultaneous
      calcineurin inhibitor withdrawal in recipients of primary renal allografts maintained
      long-term on MMF and sirolimus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
